1
00:00:09,118 --> 00:00:10,780
Oh, Tonfah ke?

2
00:00:11,063 --> 00:00:14,008
Ya. Saya belajar sini, terserempak dengan Phoon.

3
00:00:14,216 --> 00:00:16,400
Phoon ada sebut pasal Fun?

4
00:00:16,684 --> 00:00:17,927
Dah aku cakap, kan?

5
00:00:18,281 --> 00:00:20,293
Awak boleh belajar di mana saja,

6
00:00:20,474 --> 00:00:22,028
tapi jangan libatkan diri dengan Tonfah lagi.

7
00:00:22,154 --> 00:00:23,688
Dia sorok sesuatu daripada awak?

8
00:00:24,182 --> 00:00:25,040
Mungkin.

9
00:00:25,441 --> 00:00:28,908
Entahlah... macam kalau aku tersilap sikit saja,

10
00:00:29,204 --> 00:00:30,560
aku akan hilang dia selamanya.

11
00:00:30,706 --> 00:00:33,482
Awak pasti dia cuma abang awak?

12
00:00:33,831 --> 00:00:35,872
Phoon ialah adik penting P’Fah.

13
00:00:36,288 --> 00:00:39,634
Kau sedar tak kau menyakitkan hati, P’Fah?

14
00:00:43,902 --> 00:00:45,693
Untuk Thorfun.

15
00:00:52,632 --> 00:00:53,934
Akhirnya,

16
00:00:54,736 --> 00:00:57,448
Phoon pilih sakiti orang yang paling aku sayang,

17
00:00:57,690 --> 00:01:00,397
demi lindungi seorang lagi yang aku sayang.

18
00:01:01,174 --> 00:01:03,223
Sekarang, P’Fah dah bukan P’Fah yang dulu.

19
00:01:03,882 --> 00:01:06,268
Aku harap Ayah akan sayang aku lebih sikit.

20
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,435
P’Fah tanya kalau aku benci dia sekarang.

21
00:01:10,362 --> 00:01:14,444
Tak mungkin. Mati pun aku tetap sayang P’Fah.

22
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:17,358
Orang yang paling aku benci di dunia ini

23
00:01:18,014 --> 00:01:19,306
ialah diri aku sendiri.

24
00:01:21,057 --> 00:01:24,139
Dunia tanpa Fun dan P’Fah terasa susah nak hidup.

25
00:01:28,242 --> 00:01:30,210
Tapi aku dah janji dengan Fun.

26
00:01:31,789 --> 00:01:36,453
Jadi aku akan cuba hidup baik. Doakan aku, Fun.

27
00:01:53,549 --> 00:01:54,585
Pelajar tahun pertama?

28
00:01:54,946 --> 00:01:56,432
Ya, tahun pertama.

29
00:01:56,934 --> 00:01:58,106
Kena tulis nama ke?

30
00:01:59,219 --> 00:02:00,499
Mereka suruh daftar di sini.

31
00:02:03,404 --> 00:02:05,398
Err... aku Easter.

32
00:02:05,672 --> 00:02:07,008
Aku Typhoon.

33
00:02:10,481 --> 00:02:11,413
Aku belanja.

34
00:02:12,361 --> 00:02:13,365
Kenapa?

35
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,054
Sebab tadi kau tunggu aku.

36
00:02:16,373 --> 00:02:17,709
Tak apa, betul.

37
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:20,915
- Cuba dulu.
- Jadi kita tunggu siapa?

38
00:02:22,428 --> 00:02:23,558
Roommate aku.

39
00:02:25,121 --> 00:02:26,505
Mana dia pergi?

40
00:02:27,706 --> 00:02:28,693
Kenapa dia belum sampai lagi?

41
00:02:48,909 --> 00:02:50,474
Nah, baru sebut. Cepatlah.

42
00:02:59,367 --> 00:03:00,157
Phoon.

43
00:03:00,894 --> 00:03:02,605
Ini roommate aku, North.

44
00:03:03,617 --> 00:03:06,091
***North—ini Phoon, kawan aku.

45
00:03:06,167 --> 00:03:07,771
Wah, jadi aku “***North” sekarang?

46
00:03:07,897 --> 00:03:09,293
Ya, memang ngam dengan kau.

47
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,854
- Kau order aku tak manis?
- Ya.

48
00:03:12,682 --> 00:03:14,607
Aku order lebih manis.

49
00:03:15,471 --> 00:03:16,600
Aku tak suka.

50
00:03:17,143 --> 00:03:17,970
Aku suka.

51
00:03:18,165 --> 00:03:20,496
- Kalau kau suka, makan sendiri.
- Okey, tapi kau bayar.

52
00:03:21,354 --> 00:03:22,102
Lagi?

53
00:03:22,185 --> 00:03:24,103
Phoon, jangan lepak dengan orang macam ni.

54
00:03:24,875 --> 00:03:27,168
Aku North, tahun pertama kejuruteraan elektrik.

55
00:03:27,445 --> 00:03:29,804
Aku Typhoon, tahun pertama veterinar.

56
00:03:31,077 --> 00:03:33,031
- Kau dari mana?
- Phuket.

57
00:03:33,228 --> 00:03:35,432
Serius?

58
00:03:35,631 --> 00:03:39,013
Kau boleh cakap Thai Selatan?

59
00:03:39,484 --> 00:03:41,346
- Tak boleh.
- Oh, tak boleh?

60
00:03:41,354 --> 00:03:43,374
- Kau pula, North?
- Aku dari Lampang.

61
00:03:43,554 --> 00:03:48,245
Tapi aku belum pandai. Kena belajar lagi.
Nanti aku ajar, okey?

62
00:03:49,078 --> 00:03:49,866
Faham?

63
00:03:49,934 --> 00:03:51,854
Terjemah. Letak sari kata sekarang.

64
00:03:52,008 --> 00:03:53,456
Buat besar. Aku pening.

65
00:03:56,211 --> 00:03:58,077
Au maksudnya bercakap. Bo-chang maksudnya tak pandai.

66
00:03:58,336 --> 00:04:01,112
Hidup di universiti tak seteruk yang aku sangka.

67
00:04:01,634 --> 00:04:03,377
Aku rasa aku okey saja.

68
00:04:04,733 --> 00:04:06,291
Fun, kau tak perlu risau.

69
00:04:09,691 --> 00:04:11,506
Aku jumpa kawan yang baik sangat.

70
00:04:12,035 --> 00:04:13,712
Baik sangat sampai aku tertanya,

71
00:04:13,997 --> 00:04:15,506
orang macam aku ni layak ke untuk mereka.

72
00:04:18,485 --> 00:04:21,074
Bukan kau kata belok kiri? Aku ikut kau!

73
00:04:21,327 --> 00:04:23,031
Itulah kiri.

74
00:04:23,752 --> 00:04:24,682
Betul.

75
00:04:24,928 --> 00:04:28,111
Tapi kadang-kadang takdir suka mainkan orang.

76
00:04:28,395 --> 00:04:29,333
Maaf.

77
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:30,832
Apa-apalah.

78
00:04:31,518 --> 00:04:34,010
Ter kata ada orang datang ambil kita, kan?

79
00:04:34,342 --> 00:04:35,328
Jadi kita akan—

80
00:04:36,982 --> 00:04:40,583
- Kita tunggu sini.
- Sebab sejauh mana pun aku sesat,

81
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:46,573
Kau kawan Ter, kan?

82
00:04:51,471 --> 00:04:53,619
P’Fah tetap akan cari aku.

83
00:05:06,303 --> 00:05:07,550
P’Hill.

84
00:05:07,629 --> 00:05:08,198
Snek.

85
00:05:09,096 --> 00:05:11,629
- Hai, Easter.
- Hai.

86
00:05:13,431 --> 00:05:14,594
Nah, sandwic.

87
00:05:21,505 --> 00:05:23,022
- Nak?
- Ya, boleh.

88
00:07:03,216 --> 00:07:05,694
Cukup untuk hari ini. Semua boleh balik.

89
00:07:06,549 --> 00:07:08,626
Yay! Jom!

90
00:07:10,890 --> 00:07:11,826
Hei.

91
00:07:12,703 --> 00:07:14,017
Jom pergi baca hari ini.

92
00:07:14,604 --> 00:07:15,637
Rajinnya.

93
00:07:15,899 --> 00:07:17,648
Mestilah.

94
00:07:18,005 --> 00:07:21,539
P’Mhor asyik belajar, dan aku pun nak jumpa P’Hill.

95
00:07:22,699 --> 00:07:26,312
Itu nak jumpa teman lelaki, bukan belajar.
Jangan bagi alasan.

96
00:07:28,854 --> 00:07:33,481
Nah, Phoon. Kau nak ambil peperiksaan med, kan?
Aku suruh P’Mhor tutor kau.

97
00:07:33,642 --> 00:07:35,139
Tolonglah.

98
00:07:35,915 --> 00:07:38,582
Walaupun dalam hati aku tak nak kau lulus.

99
00:07:39,595 --> 00:07:41,525
Tengok tu, kutuk kawan sendiri.

100
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,961
Hei, aku bukan kutuk sesiapa.

101
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:44,888
Apa, kau nak aku berdua saja dengan kau di fakulti?

102
00:07:44,899 --> 00:07:48,230
- Apa salahnya dengan aku?
- Nampak? Inilah jadi bila aku dengan kau.

103
00:07:48,918 --> 00:07:50,717
Phoon, tengok kawan kau tu.

104
00:07:52,644 --> 00:07:54,120
Aku akan rindu kau.

105
00:07:54,638 --> 00:07:55,773
Jom, kita pergi.

106
00:07:56,792 --> 00:07:57,297
Mm.

107
00:07:57,487 --> 00:07:59,640
Ish, kau fikir lebih macam nak exam. Jom.

108
00:08:00,087 --> 00:08:04,008
- Baiklah, aku ikut.
- Betul, Foam. Kalau Phoon pergi, kau pun kena pergi.

109
00:08:05,038 --> 00:08:06,911
Tak boleh. Aku ada plan hari ini.

110
00:08:07,383 --> 00:08:08,139
Dengan siapa?

111
00:08:08,398 --> 00:08:10,108
Aku pun boleh ada plan sekali-sekala, tau.

112
00:08:10,167 --> 00:08:12,111
Kau ada plan tiap-tiap hari.

113
00:08:12,337 --> 00:08:15,733
Ingat ni—masa exam nanti suruh teman wanita kau tolong.

114
00:08:15,797 --> 00:08:16,939
Ish, berhenti membebel.

115
00:08:17,765 --> 00:08:19,829
Cepatlah, Phoon.

116
00:08:20,401 --> 00:08:21,693
Geng kita tinggal dua orang je sekarang.

117
00:08:45,229 --> 00:08:46,745
Hah? Yang lain semua mana?

118
00:08:48,333 --> 00:08:50,211
Mungkin pergi beli snek.

119
00:08:50,819 --> 00:08:53,216
- Mereka tengah datang.
- Oh.

120
00:09:01,851 --> 00:09:03,257
Kau asyik tidur je.

121
00:09:03,351 --> 00:09:04,681
Dan makan ruang aku juga.

122
00:09:09,419 --> 00:09:10,768
Memang macam tu.

123
00:09:14,884 --> 00:09:16,506
Mungkin... ini yang terbaik.

124
00:09:29,848 --> 00:09:31,334
Mak Cik Nuan.

125
00:09:38,503 --> 00:09:39,774
Ya, Mak Cik Nuan.

126
00:09:39,909 --> 00:09:41,863
Apa khabar, Phoon?

127
00:09:42,669 --> 00:09:43,754
Saya sihat.

128
00:09:44,112 --> 00:09:45,669
Mak Cik Nuan pula?

129
00:09:45,884 --> 00:09:49,859
Mak cik okey. Kenapa langsung tak hubungi mak cik?

130
00:09:50,137 --> 00:09:54,229
Maaf, Mak Cik. Saya sibuk sangat kebelakangan ini.

131
00:09:54,659 --> 00:09:58,260
Phoon, kau dah dengar? Rumah tu dah dijual.

132
00:10:00,623 --> 00:10:02,762
- Betul ke?
- Ya.

133
00:10:03,084 --> 00:10:06,539
Hari ini Mister suruh mak cik kemas barang kali terakhir.

134
00:10:06,761 --> 00:10:10,514
Masih ada barang kau, Phoon. Mak cik tak sanggup buang.

135
00:10:11,044 --> 00:10:12,891
Kau akan balik ke rumah tu?

136
00:10:17,542 --> 00:10:18,285
Ya.

137
00:10:19,045 --> 00:10:20,998
Minggu depan aku masih ada beberapa hari lapang.

138
00:10:21,317 --> 00:10:24,653
Baiklah. Telefon mak cik bila kau sampai.

139
00:10:24,902 --> 00:10:26,189
Mak cik tunggu.

140
00:10:26,705 --> 00:10:27,610
Okey.

141
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,111
Fun.

142
00:10:42,164 --> 00:10:44,351
Satu lagi bukti kenangan kita bersama...

143
00:10:45,082 --> 00:10:46,844
akan hilang tak lama lagi.

144
00:11:11,494 --> 00:11:14,047
Jadi lepas ni Mak Cik Nuan nak buat apa?

145
00:11:14,194 --> 00:11:16,437
Mungkin balik kampung dan jaga cucu.

146
00:11:17,042 --> 00:11:18,471
Mak Cik dah tua.

147
00:11:19,051 --> 00:11:21,328
Rasanya Mak Cik tak cari kerja lain.

148
00:11:22,084 --> 00:11:24,974
Baguslah. Akhirnya Mak Cik boleh rehat.

149
00:11:25,514 --> 00:11:28,688
Mak Cik besarkan saya dan Fun bertahun-tahun.

150
00:11:31,002 --> 00:11:34,401
Kita pergi jumpa Fun dulu?

151
00:11:34,835 --> 00:11:35,503
Ya.

152
00:11:48,278 --> 00:11:49,429
Mak Cik Nuan...

153
00:11:50,524 --> 00:11:53,986
Mungkin tak... Fun masih ada di sini?

154
00:11:55,875 --> 00:11:56,957
Phoon...

155
00:11:57,927 --> 00:12:00,077
Mak Cik tak nak cakap, tapi--

156
00:12:01,017 --> 00:12:01,859
tapi...

157
00:12:02,171 --> 00:12:05,493
yang dah meninggal, tetap dah pergi.

158
00:12:06,842 --> 00:12:10,524
Kalau terus berpegang, lagi sakit nanti.

159
00:12:13,711 --> 00:12:17,425
Fun pun tak nak kamu menderita.

160
00:12:31,654 --> 00:12:32,814
Fun...

161
00:12:33,805 --> 00:12:35,500
Mak Cik rindu kamu.

162
00:12:52,296 --> 00:12:53,665
Aku dah balik.

163
00:12:56,213 --> 00:12:57,287
Kau rindu aku tak?

164
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,133
Maaf sebab aku...

165
00:13:00,491 --> 00:13:02,608
tak dapat datang jumpa kau tiap hari macam dulu.

166
00:13:05,414 --> 00:13:06,672
Mesti kau sunyi sangat.

167
00:13:13,545 --> 00:13:15,066
Aku pun mimpi pasal kau, Fun.

168
00:13:16,114 --> 00:13:18,925
Dalam mimpi, rasa macam betul-betul...

169
00:13:20,042 --> 00:13:21,853
kadang-kadang aku rasa...

170
00:13:23,032 --> 00:13:24,771
kau betul-betul akan datang jumpa aku.

171
00:13:29,494 --> 00:13:31,001
Maaf sebab aku pentingkan diri.

172
00:13:33,391 --> 00:13:34,709
Kau marah aku tak, Fun,

173
00:13:35,271 --> 00:13:36,954
kalau aku berharap kau boleh tinggal?

174
00:13:40,192 --> 00:13:41,638
Aku tak nak kau pergi mana-mana pun.

175
00:14:20,198 --> 00:14:22,339
Ini saja barang Fun yang tinggal.

176
00:14:22,642 --> 00:14:23,942
Kita nak buat apa?

177
00:14:28,733 --> 00:14:30,318
Boleh kita dermakan?

178
00:14:31,111 --> 00:14:32,265
Tak apa ke?

179
00:14:32,903 --> 00:14:34,124
Saya rasa...

180
00:14:34,911 --> 00:14:37,702
Fun nak barang ni bermanfaat untuk orang lain.

181
00:14:39,871 --> 00:14:42,167
Mak Cik tak pasti patut cakap atau tak,

182
00:14:43,105 --> 00:14:44,592
tapi ada sesuatu

183
00:14:45,204 --> 00:14:46,992
Mak Cik nak kamu tahu.

184
00:14:48,694 --> 00:14:49,840
Apa dia?

185
00:14:51,690 --> 00:14:53,751
Fun dah tahu dari awal

186
00:14:54,062 --> 00:14:56,776
kamu bukan anak kandung keluarga ni.

187
00:15:00,727 --> 00:15:01,647
Betul ke?

188
00:15:04,038 --> 00:15:09,560
Malam tu, saya dan Fun terdengar Miss dan Mister bergaduh.

189
00:15:11,545 --> 00:15:15,662
Saya takut Fun tak dapat terima,

190
00:15:17,134 --> 00:15:18,595
tapi rupanya...

191
00:15:19,158 --> 00:15:20,440
Fun...

192
00:15:20,835 --> 00:15:22,878
tetap sayang kamu macam biasa.

193
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,567
Tapi lepas Fun meninggal dunia,

194
00:15:29,054 --> 00:15:31,133
semua mula jadi berantakan.

195
00:15:32,037 --> 00:15:34,940
Mak Cik pun tak tahu nak buat apa.

196
00:15:38,205 --> 00:15:41,444
Phoon, bukan kamu yang hancurkan keluarga ni.

197
00:15:42,810 --> 00:15:45,120
Fun tak pernah fikir macam tu.

198
00:15:47,521 --> 00:15:49,296
Tolong jangan salahkan diri sendiri.

199
00:15:56,451 --> 00:15:57,531
Terima kasih.

200
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:46,278
Kebenaran yang Mak Cik nak kamu tengok... semua ni.

201
00:16:47,293 --> 00:16:49,958
Mister suruh Mak Cik buang semua ni.

202
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,623
Tapi Mak Cik simpan diam-diam.

203
00:16:54,927 --> 00:16:56,237
Apa benda ni?

204
00:16:59,470 --> 00:17:03,348
Benda ni dihantar sejak kamu umur setahun, Phoon.

205
00:17:03,930 --> 00:17:05,631
Setiap tahun.

206
00:17:06,087 --> 00:17:07,524
Sekitar bulan Mac.

207
00:17:08,647 --> 00:17:10,247
Bulan lahir kamu.

208
00:17:11,927 --> 00:17:14,303
Tak ada nama pengirim, tapi...

209
00:17:14,774 --> 00:17:15,927
ada nama penerima.

210
00:17:20,613 --> 00:17:21,570
Ibu saya?

211
00:17:24,757 --> 00:17:28,740
Miss dah buang banyak yang lain.

212
00:17:29,047 --> 00:17:32,588
Ini saja yang Mak Cik sempat simpan diam-diam.

213
00:17:38,548 --> 00:17:39,656
Tak apa.

214
00:17:40,398 --> 00:17:41,600
Ini dah cukup.

215
00:17:42,814 --> 00:17:44,280
Terima kasih, Mak Cik Nuan.

216
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:51,102
Mak Cik harap betullah macam yang kamu fikir.

217
00:17:52,074 --> 00:17:55,484
Sekurang-kurangnya ibu kandung kamu masih ingat kamu.

218
00:17:56,508 --> 00:17:59,742
Tapi mesti ada sebab...

219
00:18:00,023 --> 00:18:02,002
yang buat dia tak dapat datang jumpa kamu.

220
00:18:06,028 --> 00:18:06,897
Ya.

221
00:18:07,739 --> 00:18:09,456
Aku harap dia ada sebab.

222
00:18:10,574 --> 00:18:12,100
Apa-apa sebab pun.

223
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,640
Asalkan bukan sebab dia tak sayang aku.

224
00:19:06,573 --> 00:19:08,920
Dah balik dari Phuket?

225
00:19:08,937 --> 00:19:10,691
Ya, baru sampai bilik.

226
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,300
Kita nak buat makan-makan malam ni.

227
00:19:13,328 --> 00:19:14,850
Sempena apa?

228
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:17,423
Sempena kita rasa nak makan.

229
00:19:19,124 --> 00:19:21,078
Siapa pergi?

230
00:19:21,490 --> 00:19:24,266
Aku, North, P’Hill, dan kawan-kawan P’Hill.

231
00:19:28,164 --> 00:19:29,343
Kawan-kawan P’Hill?

232
00:19:29,724 --> 00:19:32,422
Ya, ramai. Mesti seronok.

233
00:19:38,481 --> 00:19:39,242
Tapi...

234
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:45,722
Okeylah, aku pergi.

235
00:19:46,216 --> 00:19:47,970
Bagus. Aku ambil kau.

236
00:19:48,666 --> 00:19:50,001
Mm, okey.

237
00:19:58,731 --> 00:20:00,145
Jadi kau pergi ke tak?

238
00:20:00,777 --> 00:20:02,056
Rasanya aku tak pergi.

239
00:20:02,597 --> 00:20:03,694
Sebab Phoon?

240
00:20:06,188 --> 00:20:07,152
Ya.

241
00:20:08,042 --> 00:20:10,020
Dia mungkin lebih selesa kalau aku tak pergi.

242
00:20:10,909 --> 00:20:13,844
Kau patut bincang elok-elok. Janggal sangat.

243
00:20:14,682 --> 00:20:16,330
Dia nak bercakap dengan aku ke?

244
00:20:17,850 --> 00:20:21,668
Muka aku pun dia tak pandang.

245
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:27,595
Okey, aku berhenti. Kau jadi macam ni bila sebut Phoon.

246
00:20:27,877 --> 00:20:29,764
Aku cakap pada mereka kau sibuk.

247
00:20:30,269 --> 00:20:31,137
Mm.

248
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:45,871
P’Fah, tengok. Langit cantik sangat hari ni.

249
00:20:46,625 --> 00:20:48,311
Padahal semalam hujan lebat sangat.

250
00:20:49,573 --> 00:20:53,198
Baguslah langit boleh buat kau senyum macam ni.

251
00:21:15,231 --> 00:21:15,960
Hei!

252
00:21:16,694 --> 00:21:17,934
Jadi Fah pergi mana sebenarnya?

253
00:21:18,262 --> 00:21:19,216
Dia sibuk.

254
00:21:19,545 --> 00:21:20,688
Sibuk apa maksudnya?

255
00:21:21,007 --> 00:21:23,743
Kenapa banyak tanya? Sibuk tu sibuklah.

256
00:21:23,754 --> 00:21:25,118
Kau menyakitkan hati betul.

257
00:21:25,238 --> 00:21:27,231
Sial, Jo, aku cakap dua ayat je.

258
00:21:27,574 --> 00:21:29,271
- Kurang ajar.
- Kurang ajar?

259
00:21:29,414 --> 00:21:30,515
Kurang ajar macam mana?

260
00:21:31,085 --> 00:21:32,269
Hill, tengok dia kacau aku.

261
00:21:38,149 --> 00:21:40,001
Hei, bukan kau kata kau sibuk?

262
00:21:48,441 --> 00:21:50,875
Lagi aku fikir, lagi aku rasa bebas tu lebih baik.

263
00:21:52,619 --> 00:21:53,952
Apa maksud “bebas tu lebih baik”?

264
00:21:56,946 --> 00:22:00,198
Arthit, aku nak duduk sini.

265
00:22:02,797 --> 00:22:05,951
Apa masalah kau? Banyak tempat—pergi duduk tempat lain.

266
00:22:06,041 --> 00:22:08,090
Pergi duduk sebelah Jo. Skandal kau.

267
00:22:09,151 --> 00:22:10,179
Jo? Skandal aku?

268
00:22:10,311 --> 00:22:11,016
Ya.

269
00:22:11,804 --> 00:22:12,724
Yang kurang ajar ni?

270
00:22:12,909 --> 00:22:14,408
Dah, cepatlah.

271
00:22:15,949 --> 00:22:17,397
Aku buat ni semata-mata untuk kau.

272
00:22:18,431 --> 00:22:19,685
Aku pun tak nak duduk situ.

273
00:22:20,234 --> 00:22:21,200
Sebelah si berlagak tu.

274
00:22:29,260 --> 00:22:30,354
Nak pindah meja lain?

275
00:22:35,124 --> 00:22:36,042
Hei.

276
00:22:37,656 --> 00:22:39,100
Lama tak jumpa.

277
00:22:45,059 --> 00:22:45,811
Ya.

278
00:22:58,223 --> 00:22:59,456
Phoon, nak udang?

279
00:23:00,801 --> 00:23:02,007
- Hah?
- Hati-hati, meleleh.

280
00:23:02,395 --> 00:23:03,752
Nampak sedap gila. Kongsi sikit.

281
00:23:03,841 --> 00:23:05,118
- Kongsi apa?
- Udang tu.

282
00:23:05,140 --> 00:23:07,112
- Udang apa?
- Yang kau kupas sekarang tu.

283
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:08,654
Kalau nak udang, pesan sendiri.

284
00:23:08,684 --> 00:23:10,647
Wah, North, beraninya kau.

285
00:23:10,758 --> 00:23:12,967
Aku tak pernah merungut kau makan barang aku.

286
00:23:13,179 --> 00:23:14,634
- Barang dalam peti sejuk?
- Ya.

287
00:23:15,653 --> 00:23:18,417
Bukan kau beli untuk kongsi ke?

288
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,478
Kongsi?

289
00:23:20,841 --> 00:23:21,788
- Kongsi dengan kau?
- Ya.

290
00:23:21,804 --> 00:23:24,561
- Kau yang mencuri.
- Lain kali cakap je.

291
00:23:24,625 --> 00:23:26,389
Adab asas, kena minta dulu.

292
00:23:26,602 --> 00:23:27,922
Sejak bila aku ada adab?

293
00:23:27,992 --> 00:23:29,357
- Memang tak ada.
- Tepat.

294
00:23:29,379 --> 00:23:30,845
- Bagi aku.
- Jangan makan.

295
00:23:31,008 --> 00:23:32,487
Dua ekor. Kupaskan sekali.

296
00:23:33,508 --> 00:23:34,280
Asyik aku je.

297
00:23:34,542 --> 00:23:35,641
Bagus.

298
00:23:37,690 --> 00:23:39,342
Hei, kupas elok-elok.

299
00:23:45,902 --> 00:23:47,309
Udang. Udang je. Buat kemas sikit.

300
00:23:49,903 --> 00:23:50,936
Terima kasih.

301
00:24:06,462 --> 00:24:09,503
Hei, kenapa lama sangat nak bayar?

302
00:24:09,804 --> 00:24:10,705
Ya, betul.

303
00:24:11,822 --> 00:24:15,266
Atau P’Mhor tengah gaduh siapa bayar?

304
00:24:16,309 --> 00:24:18,509
Yang pasti, P’Arthit bukan salah seorang.

305
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:23,927
Phoon.

306
00:24:24,219 --> 00:24:24,654
Hm?

307
00:24:26,765 --> 00:24:29,136
Aku nak tanya kau sesuatu.

308
00:24:32,571 --> 00:24:35,438
Aduh, kau melengah lagi. Bila nak tanya?

309
00:24:35,546 --> 00:24:36,536
Aku tanya.

310
00:24:36,739 --> 00:24:38,309
- Jadi apa hal kau dengan P’Fah?
- Hah?

311
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:41,986
Sial, North. Kau memang terus terang.

312
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,768
Mana aku tahu nak jawab macam mana?

313
00:24:43,982 --> 00:24:45,434
Kau asyik “uh... uh...” macam tu.

314
00:24:48,442 --> 00:24:51,026
Ceritanya panjang.

315
00:24:51,285 --> 00:24:52,905
Korang sedia nak dengar?

316
00:24:53,259 --> 00:24:55,271
Sedia. Memang sedia.

317
00:24:56,288 --> 00:24:57,734
Ya, teruskan.

318
00:25:01,946 --> 00:25:02,829
Jadi...

319
00:25:04,718 --> 00:25:05,868
Jadi?

320
00:25:06,368 --> 00:25:08,518
Aku dengan P’Fah...

321
00:25:08,663 --> 00:25:10,222
Ya? Kenapa?

322
00:25:11,122 --> 00:25:12,232
Korang tengah cakap pasal apa?

323
00:25:12,500 --> 00:25:15,040
Oh—tak ada apa, P’Hill.

324
00:25:15,238 --> 00:25:16,505
Aku dah kenyang. Jom balik.

325
00:25:16,577 --> 00:25:18,488
Bye, P’. Bye.

326
00:25:18,574 --> 00:25:19,998
Bye, P’Hill.

327
00:25:20,259 --> 00:25:21,491
Jumpa lagi.

328
00:25:22,474 --> 00:25:23,998
Tadi korang cakap pasal apa?

329
00:25:25,231 --> 00:25:28,068
Hmm... rahsia tahap tertinggi.

330
00:25:28,485 --> 00:25:29,949
Kalau nak tahu, pindah duit dulu.

331
00:25:31,211 --> 00:25:32,121
Pergi ambil kat rumah.

332
00:25:35,789 --> 00:25:37,002
Aku gerak dulu.

333
00:25:37,034 --> 00:25:38,324
P’Jo, dah transfer belum?

334
00:25:38,368 --> 00:25:40,754
- Aku ikut kau, Jo.
- Kenapa kau ikut?

335
00:26:29,115 --> 00:26:30,539
Dao? Macam mana kau sampai sini?

336
00:26:30,586 --> 00:26:32,991
Tara!

337
00:26:33,226 --> 00:26:34,302
Aku yang telefon dia.

338
00:26:34,619 --> 00:26:39,717
Aku rasa masalah kau ni besar sangat untuk aku dan North je.

339
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:43,287
Jangan cakap semua yang muncul pagi ni—

340
00:26:43,783 --> 00:26:45,703
sebab aku dengan P’Fah?

341
00:26:45,832 --> 00:26:46,802
Ya.

342
00:26:48,506 --> 00:26:50,376
Nak buat aku tunggu lama mana? Masuk.

343
00:26:51,377 --> 00:26:53,946
- Baiklah.
- Masuklah, Dao. Jangan segan.

344
00:26:54,656 --> 00:26:55,988
Hei, kau tak nak ambil snek ke?

345
00:26:57,099 --> 00:26:58,285
Cepatlah, aku lapar gila.

346
00:26:59,256 --> 00:27:01,127
Okey, korang. Mula cakap.

347
00:27:01,268 --> 00:27:03,819
Hari ni tak payah tunggu Foam. Dia pilih tidur.

348
00:27:04,054 --> 00:27:06,970
Fikir—antara kawan dan tidur, dia pilih tidur.

349
00:27:07,186 --> 00:27:09,822
Kau pula? Antara kawan dan makan, pilih mana?

350
00:27:10,128 --> 00:27:13,395
- Aku pilih “antara”.
- Pilih apa? Cakap jelas.

351
00:27:13,955 --> 00:27:14,770
Aku pilih semua.

352
00:27:16,531 --> 00:27:17,871
Aku bagi kau satu peluang lagi.

353
00:27:18,342 --> 00:27:20,395
Baik—makan dengan kawan.

354
00:27:21,620 --> 00:27:22,717
Kau ni kuat makan.

355
00:27:22,764 --> 00:27:24,103
Sudahlah, North.

356
00:27:25,580 --> 00:27:26,645
Kau tak nak makan ke?

357
00:27:31,555 --> 00:27:33,271
Okey, jom mula.

358
00:27:35,115 --> 00:27:36,971
Sebab kita semua ada sini hari ni—

359
00:27:37,071 --> 00:27:37,880
Mm.

360
00:27:38,405 --> 00:27:39,435
Jadi apa sebenarnya?

361
00:27:42,071 --> 00:27:43,041
Pasal aku.

362
00:27:46,517 --> 00:27:49,900
Ya, aku tahu pasal kau—tapi boleh cerita tak?

363
00:27:50,598 --> 00:27:51,754
Pasal aku.

364
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:54,592
Cerita aku.

365
00:27:54,807 --> 00:27:56,685
Baiklah. Aku tak tanya lebih.

366
00:27:58,205 --> 00:28:00,216
Aku cuma tak tahu nak jelaskan—macam—

367
00:28:00,437 --> 00:28:01,668
Relaks, Maew. Aku bergurau je.

368
00:28:02,266 --> 00:28:03,225
Jadi apa?

369
00:28:04,217 --> 00:28:05,179
Boleh cerita?

370
00:28:06,075 --> 00:28:07,016
Ini rahsia ke?

371
00:28:09,465 --> 00:28:10,604
Rahsia besar?

372
00:28:11,755 --> 00:28:13,192
Besar sangat.

373
00:28:14,014 --> 00:28:15,674
Aku tak nak sesiapa tahu.

374
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,162
Terutamanya...

375
00:28:17,804 --> 00:28:18,749
P’Mhor.

376
00:28:23,105 --> 00:28:24,315
Tapi aku ada satu permintaan.

377
00:28:24,951 --> 00:28:26,065
Lepas aku beritahu—

378
00:28:26,894 --> 00:28:28,638
jangan benci aku, okey?

379
00:28:30,780 --> 00:28:32,151
Kami tak benci kau.

380
00:28:32,696 --> 00:28:34,943
Walau kau cakar kami, kami tak benci.

381
00:28:36,114 --> 00:28:37,659
Kau sendiri cakap—ingat tu.

382
00:28:37,882 --> 00:28:39,260
Mana tahu satu hari kau rasa nak cakar kami.

383
00:28:39,914 --> 00:28:42,260
Ya, tak ada siapa akan benci kau.

384
00:28:43,481 --> 00:28:45,591
- Kau boleh relaks.
- Jadi—

385
00:28:46,567 --> 00:28:49,044
- Mula cakap.
- Ya, teruskan.

386
00:29:14,971 --> 00:29:17,960
Jadi sebab tu kau suka ambil gambar langit, kan?

387
00:29:21,317 --> 00:29:22,826
Sebab kau suka P’Fah.

388
00:29:24,794 --> 00:29:26,678
Sejujurnya, lepas dengar semua—

389
00:29:27,117 --> 00:29:31,506
apa masalah ayah kau sebenarnya?

390
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:34,186
Dengar pun dah buat aku marah.

391
00:29:36,602 --> 00:29:38,475
Terima kasih sebab marah untuk pihak aku.

392
00:29:38,736 --> 00:29:40,531
Ya... bukan semua orang

393
00:29:41,191 --> 00:29:42,882
bersedia jadi ibu bapa.

394
00:29:43,564 --> 00:29:44,491
Tapi tetap—

395
00:29:44,961 --> 00:29:46,805
dia dah jadi ayah aku.

396
00:29:47,997 --> 00:29:50,543
Dan dia satu-satunya yang aku ada.

397
00:29:52,561 --> 00:29:55,331
Ya... kau memang kuat.

398
00:29:56,985 --> 00:29:58,792
- Aku?
- Ya.

399
00:29:59,219 --> 00:30:01,306
Lepas semua tu, kau masih boleh senyum.

400
00:30:01,811 --> 00:30:03,158
Kau memang hebat.

401
00:30:05,860 --> 00:30:06,545
Ah.

402
00:30:07,026 --> 00:30:10,259
Hei, tak apa. Mari, peluk ramai-ramai.

403
00:30:12,071 --> 00:30:13,980
- Aduh!
- Aku pun nak join.

404
00:30:17,650 --> 00:30:18,925
Terima kasih, semua.

405
00:30:23,442 --> 00:30:25,284
Okey, okey.

406
00:30:27,703 --> 00:30:28,830
Jadi... siapa pujuk siapa ni?

407
00:30:29,214 --> 00:30:30,512
Sedih je, okey?

408
00:30:30,591 --> 00:30:32,905
Alah, bukan cerita kau pun.

409
00:30:40,023 --> 00:30:40,890
Tak apa.

410
00:30:45,285 --> 00:30:46,484
Itu P’Fun?

411
00:30:48,339 --> 00:30:49,100
Ya.

412
00:30:54,331 --> 00:30:55,685
Kau masih letak gambar tu macam ni.

413
00:30:56,435 --> 00:30:57,742
Kau tak rindu dia teruk ke?

414
00:30:58,585 --> 00:30:59,851
Aku rindu dia sangat.

415
00:31:01,139 --> 00:31:02,911
Air mata aku keluar lagi—pause dulu.

416
00:31:05,728 --> 00:31:06,407
Hei!

417
00:31:06,856 --> 00:31:08,331
Aku ada idea bagus untuk kau.

418
00:31:12,028 --> 00:31:13,168
Nah.

419
00:31:17,509 --> 00:31:18,251
Nah.

420
00:31:19,226 --> 00:31:20,358
Apa kata kita letak gambar kita pula?

421
00:31:21,342 --> 00:31:22,490
Bukan itu idea tak bagus?

422
00:31:27,585 --> 00:31:30,253
Sini—kat sini.
Kau roh penjaga, jadi duduk bawah ni.

423
00:31:30,474 --> 00:31:32,180
Ah—wei!

424
00:31:35,367 --> 00:31:37,177
Jadi aku kena belajar sambil tengok muka korang?

425
00:31:37,391 --> 00:31:38,816
- Tepat.
- Ya.

426
00:31:39,001 --> 00:31:40,536
Macam kami temankan kau.

427
00:31:41,444 --> 00:31:42,466
Baguslah.

428
00:31:42,502 --> 00:31:44,595
Dia macam suka.

429
00:31:44,715 --> 00:31:46,475
- Tapi jangan minta lagi.
- Ya.

430
00:31:46,792 --> 00:31:47,745
Itu je yang aku ada.

431
00:31:48,228 --> 00:31:49,062
Satu gambar je.

432
00:31:54,693 --> 00:31:57,082
Jadi kau nak buat apa pasal P’Fah?

433
00:31:59,032 --> 00:32:00,259
Sejujurnya aku pun tak tahu lagi.

434
00:32:01,333 --> 00:32:03,598
Kau nak biar jadi janggal macam ni je?

435
00:32:04,404 --> 00:32:05,782
Cuma...

436
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,204
bukan idea yang bagus.

437
00:32:07,804 --> 00:32:09,125
Terlalu janggal.

438
00:32:09,822 --> 00:32:11,842
Ya, aku perasan.

439
00:32:12,048 --> 00:32:13,402
Aku rasa kau dengan P’Fah...

440
00:32:13,607 --> 00:32:16,245
- pelik.
- Kau rasa P’Fah marah aku, North?

441
00:32:16,450 --> 00:32:17,851
Sebab tolak dia macam tu?

442
00:32:19,068 --> 00:32:20,190
Kalau aku?

443
00:32:20,908 --> 00:32:22,087
Aku dah tumbuk kau.

444
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:26,277
- Seteruk tu?
- Seteruk tu. Mulut kau tu memang patut.

445
00:32:26,327 --> 00:32:27,777
Kalau macam tu, kau yang pertama beratur.

446
00:32:29,125 --> 00:32:31,828
- Mungkin aku memang patut kena tumbuk.
- Ya, mari sini muka kau.

447
00:32:33,482 --> 00:32:35,977
- Baik.
- Wei, kau buat apa?

448
00:32:36,242 --> 00:32:38,829
Dia nak kena tumbuk, boleh?

449
00:32:38,887 --> 00:32:40,657
Kau buat dia takut. Mari sini.

450
00:32:46,430 --> 00:32:48,080
Aku asyik fikir pasal ni.

451
00:32:48,850 --> 00:32:50,630
Yang aku boleh lupakan P’Fah.

452
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:53,250
Kalau aku menjauh, benda ni patut habis.

453
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:56,080
Tapi lagi kerap kami jumpa,

454
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,950
lagi rasa makin jauh.

455
00:33:01,650 --> 00:33:02,990
Aku rasa aku menyesal.

456
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:04,910
Sebab semuanya tak boleh jadi macam dulu.

457
00:33:06,650 --> 00:33:08,260
Dan ia sakit.

458
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:11,470
Kalau akhirnya aku kena kehilangan P’Fah.

459
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:16,910
Jadi “dulu” tu macam mana?

460
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:18,130
Err...

461
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:20,120
Kami saling jaga.

462
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:22,740
Kami saling risau. Niat kami baik.

463
00:33:24,050 --> 00:33:25,660
Aku cuma nak dia tahu yang...

464
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,760
kalau dia tak ada sesiapa,

465
00:33:28,320 --> 00:33:29,670
dan dia berpaling,

466
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,720
dia akan jumpa aku kat sini.

467
00:33:34,250 --> 00:33:36,250
tak kira aku siapa dalam hidup dia.

468
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:41,460
Tak kira kau siapa dalam hidup dia?

469
00:33:48,610 --> 00:33:49,670
Aku dah dapat.

470
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:53,010
Cara untuk Maew bercakap dengan P’Fah,

471
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:54,580
untuk jaga dia,

472
00:33:54,970 --> 00:33:57,870
dan buat P’Fah tahu ada orang ambil peduli.

473
00:34:01,260 --> 00:34:02,090
Apa dia?

474
00:34:08,030 --> 00:34:08,840
Dia dah sampai.

475
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:11,710
Wei!

476
00:34:15,350 --> 00:34:18,200
Cuba ingat—apa benda pertama kau bagi P’Fah?

477
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:20,170
- Apa?
- Sandwic dan susu coklat.

478
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:22,480
Tak terlalu biasa ke?

479
00:34:23,270 --> 00:34:25,790
Aku tak tahu dia suka apa, jadi aku beli yang aku suka.

480
00:34:26,750 --> 00:34:28,650
Tapi aku rasa P’Fah akan suka.

481
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,830
Wei, aku dah semak semula dengan P’Hill.

482
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,040
Kau boleh ambil barang tu

483
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,490
dan letak sebelum kelas.

484
00:34:35,830 --> 00:34:36,600
Mm.

485
00:34:37,940 --> 00:34:39,600
Kau dah tulis surat untuk dia?

486
00:34:40,050 --> 00:34:40,780
Dah.

487
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,260
Tengok? Gambar senyum.

488
00:34:45,610 --> 00:34:47,480
Walau tak letak harapan, aku tetap kecewa.

489
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:51,070
Kenapa tak tulis mesej sikit?
Biar dia tahu perasaan kau.

490
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:55,730
Ini kali pertama. Aku tak tahu nak tulis apa.

491
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,740
Err... Hai.

492
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,440
Itu terlalu biasa.

493
00:35:00,830 --> 00:35:04,600
Kau kena tulis lebih sikit,
baru dia ingat kau.

494
00:35:05,250 --> 00:35:07,160
P’Fah, aku suka kau gila-gila.

495
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:09,080
Wei, itu boleh!

496
00:35:09,170 --> 00:35:10,330
Aku bergurau.

497
00:35:10,630 --> 00:35:11,500
Ish.

498
00:35:11,930 --> 00:35:13,080
Tapi kami setuju.

499
00:35:13,390 --> 00:35:16,080
Kami rasa dia akan rasa kelakar sikit.

500
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:20,040
Ya, tulis je. Percayalah.

501
00:35:21,490 --> 00:35:22,850
Okey.

502
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:26,930
Come on, kau dah latihan tiru tulisan, kan? Tunjuk.

503
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:29,560
Aku

504
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:31,090
betul-betul suka P'

505
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,460
sangat.

506
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:37,900
Tapi kalau panggil “P’,” dia tahu kita budak tahun pertama.

507
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,170
Ya.

508
00:35:43,340 --> 00:35:45,110
Aku rasa kau patut tulis “awak”.

509
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:47,030
Macam tu dia tak tahu senior ke junior.

510
00:35:47,270 --> 00:35:47,810
Kan?

511
00:35:48,050 --> 00:35:49,960
- “Awak”?
- Ya, tulis “awak”. Lagi bagus.

512
00:35:50,090 --> 00:35:51,690
Pandai sekali-sekala.

513
00:35:51,970 --> 00:35:53,190
Sepanjang hidup aku.

514
00:35:54,350 --> 00:35:57,130
Aku betul-betul, betul-betul suka awak.

515
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:58,910
Sangat.

516
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:00,910
- Ya.
- Itu. Tepat.

517
00:36:01,120 --> 00:36:02,290
Jom buat.

518
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:05,500
Jom. Jom.

519
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:09,780
Kau rasa cara ni betul-betul jadi?

520
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:13,550
Kau dah sampai sini. Tak boleh undur dah.

521
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:16,400
Atau kalau Maew belum sedia, kita datang hari lain?

522
00:36:16,670 --> 00:36:17,920
Hari ni.

523
00:36:18,490 --> 00:36:19,660
Yakin sikit.

524
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:21,800
Jomlah.

525
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,240
Wei, P’Arthit.

526
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:36,380
Kau buat aku terkejut gila.

527
00:36:39,730 --> 00:36:40,660
Kita nak buat apa?

528
00:36:41,890 --> 00:36:43,820
Phoon, sekarang masanya.

529
00:36:44,080 --> 00:36:46,070
Letak kat situ. Dia nampak nanti.

530
00:36:46,270 --> 00:36:48,670
Dia akan bagi pada P’Fah sendiri. Pergi.

531
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:50,570
Sekarang.

532
00:36:50,830 --> 00:36:51,590
Sial.

533
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,170
P’Fah ada beratus kawan.

534
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:55,290
Kenapa mesti si dungu ni yang nak kencing?

535
00:36:56,650 --> 00:36:57,970
Jadi memang si dungu ni lah.

536
00:36:58,650 --> 00:36:59,600
- Atas aku.
- Hah?

537
00:37:03,830 --> 00:37:04,710
Hati-hati, okey?

538
00:37:06,560 --> 00:37:08,950
- North, jangan main-main. Cepat.
- Relaks.

539
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:14,510
Lain kali kau turun guna tali je.

540
00:38:09,620 --> 00:38:11,090
Kepada: Tonfah

541
00:38:14,050 --> 00:38:15,560
Kau ingat aku rider penghantar ke apa?

542
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,090
Wei!

543
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:34,280
- Apa?!
- Dia terus makan.

544
00:38:37,570 --> 00:38:38,630
Apa masalah dia?

545
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:40,970
Kenapa pula?

546
00:38:41,210 --> 00:38:42,220
Tak apa.

547
00:38:44,390 --> 00:38:45,250
Tak apa, bro.

548
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,160
Itu snek je.

549
00:38:47,790 --> 00:38:49,930
Tapi surat tu patut sampai pada dia.

550
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,250
Ya.

551
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,190
Rasanya.

552
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:53,100
Tunggu—

553
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:55,490
Entah, kalau dia makan surat tu sekali?

554
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:57,120
Mana ada orang makan surat, North?

555
00:38:57,870 --> 00:38:59,380
Nama dia Arthit, kan?

556
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,160
Ya, kawan P’Fah.

557
00:39:01,430 --> 00:39:02,620
Perangai teruk.

558
00:39:03,210 --> 00:39:05,520
Kalau dia baik, dia makan barang orang macam tu ke?

559
00:39:14,530 --> 00:39:15,440
Fah.

560
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:16,900
Ada orang tinggalkan ni untuk kau.

561
00:39:20,850 --> 00:39:22,960
- Sedap?
- Ya, sedap.

562
00:39:24,570 --> 00:39:27,770
Hari ni dah berapa kali?
Kau ramai peminat kebelakangan ni.

563
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:29,880
Ya.

564
00:39:32,330 --> 00:39:33,150
Buka.

565
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,340
Aku ingat kau dah makan semua.

566
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:37,630
Ada lagi.

567
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,380
Wei, susu masih ada.

568
00:39:57,680 --> 00:39:58,850
Aku betul-betul suka awak sangat.

569
00:40:00,470 --> 00:40:01,690
Kau senyum pasal apa?

570
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:04,810
Tak ada apa.

571
00:40:05,390 --> 00:40:06,340
Comel.

572
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:28,070
Dah jadi?

573
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:38,210
Cakap pasal dia, dia muncul.

574
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:45,590
Kita mula misi seterusnya esok.

575
00:40:46,010 --> 00:40:50,410
Aku nak maklumkan, aku dah cari penghantar.

576
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:54,270
Bobby sanggup hantar tiap pagi, tukar satu tin kola.

577
00:40:54,750 --> 00:41:01,480
Aku jamin P’Fah takkan dapat kesan kau. Tamat.

578
00:41:06,450 --> 00:41:08,250
Diterima. Tamat!

579
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:23,730
Kenapa susu coklat pula?

580
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,330
Sebab aku suka.

581
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:26,860
Dan kau beli satu je?

582
00:41:27,860 --> 00:41:31,610
- Aku boleh je beli semua.
- Wah, kaya betul.

583
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:34,990
Hoi!

584
00:41:41,120 --> 00:41:42,250
Yang tu Bobby punya.

585
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,400
Siapa Bobby?

586
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:46,970
Cupid.

587
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:48,810
Maksud aku, Bobby.

588
00:41:48,970 --> 00:41:51,220
Dia kawan sepupu aku.

589
00:41:51,450 --> 00:41:52,830
Saudara jauh, dan—

590
00:41:54,180 --> 00:41:54,720
Hah?

591
00:41:57,370 --> 00:41:59,670
Jadi, Bobby tu—

592
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:06,040
Satu pun okey.

593
00:42:07,330 --> 00:42:09,400
Satu pun dah cukup untuk P’Arthit.

594
00:42:11,410 --> 00:42:12,630
Daripada buang, baik bagi.

595
00:42:12,650 --> 00:42:13,330
Ya.

596
00:42:17,240 --> 00:42:19,910
Pasal surat tu—

597
00:42:20,060 --> 00:42:21,680
Kau dah tahu nak tulis apa?

598
00:42:22,990 --> 00:42:24,120
Hmm.

599
00:42:26,670 --> 00:42:27,670
Sejujurnya, aku pun tak tahu lagi.

600
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:37,690
Jangan lupa. Surat pertama kena padu,
baru dia ingat kau.

601
00:42:39,380 --> 00:42:40,470
Cukuplah.

602
00:42:41,740 --> 00:42:43,110
Kenapa nak besarkan sangat?

603
00:42:44,890 --> 00:42:47,180
Supaya P’Fah terkesan.

604
00:42:54,410 --> 00:42:55,620
Aku cuba.

605
00:42:59,470 --> 00:43:01,410
Berani kau keluarkan snek aku?

606
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:08,930
Mana suratnya?

607
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:11,130
Ni. Aku nak tulis sekarang.

608
00:43:20,290 --> 00:43:22,520
Cepatlah. Aku ada kelas, tau.

609
00:43:27,190 --> 00:43:28,930
Macam mana tulisan aku?

610
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:33,740
- Nampak natural?
- Eh, jadi. Nampak meyakinkan.

611
00:43:34,180 --> 00:43:35,760
Kau pandai juga tiru tulisan.

612
00:43:36,860 --> 00:43:37,940
Tak pelik, kan?

613
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:39,610
Heh. Sempurna.

614
00:43:46,590 --> 00:43:47,670
Bagi ni pada Bobby juga.

615
00:43:48,280 --> 00:43:49,360
Baik, diterima.

616
00:43:49,650 --> 00:43:50,610
Serah pada aku.

617
00:43:51,580 --> 00:43:52,510
Hei.

618
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:54,040
Jumpa lagi.

619
00:44:15,640 --> 00:44:16,610
P’Fah.

620
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:21,790
Err… ada orang suruh saya bagi ni pada awak.

621
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,290
Ya.

622
00:44:43,770 --> 00:44:44,530
Terima kasih.

623
00:45:11,850 --> 00:45:15,680
Pagi ni cuaca elok.
Langit pun cerah.

624
00:45:16,040 --> 00:45:17,760
Matahari tak terik sangat.

625
00:45:18,370 --> 00:45:20,420
Permulaan hari yang baik.

626
00:45:20,530 --> 00:45:23,160
Harap awak gembira sepanjang hari.

627
00:45:41,670 --> 00:45:44,980
Bobby tu hantar terus pada P’Fah sendiri.

628
00:45:45,440 --> 00:45:47,610
Jadi P’Fah cakap apa?

629
00:45:48,380 --> 00:45:49,300
Dia tak cakap apa-apa.

630
00:45:52,240 --> 00:45:52,880
Okey.

631
00:45:53,130 --> 00:45:55,540
Tak apa. Kau baru mula.

632
00:45:55,660 --> 00:45:56,230
Ya.

633
00:45:56,290 --> 00:45:58,670
Kau sedar tak ramai orang hantar benda tiap hari?

634
00:45:59,210 --> 00:46:02,130
Betul. Benda macam ni kena konsisten.

635
00:46:02,310 --> 00:46:04,370
Kalau kau terus hantar, lama-lama dia cair.

636
00:46:04,470 --> 00:46:05,270
Tepat.

637
00:46:05,640 --> 00:46:06,560
Tapi—

638
00:46:07,060 --> 00:46:09,720
Sejujurnya, aku tak nak bersaing dengan sesiapa.

639
00:46:11,940 --> 00:46:14,500
Aku cuma nak ada di sisi P’Fah, apa cara pun.

640
00:46:15,520 --> 00:46:17,910
Lagipun ramai orang suka dia.

641
00:46:18,510 --> 00:46:20,490
Aku rasa tak semestinya aku.

642
00:46:21,630 --> 00:46:25,620
- Tapi mustahil tak berharap, kan?
- Harap.

643
00:46:26,370 --> 00:46:27,230
Hmm…

644
00:46:27,990 --> 00:46:29,100
Sikit je.

645
00:46:29,300 --> 00:46:31,340
Sikit je, betul.

646
00:46:32,460 --> 00:46:34,210
Ya, jadi—

647
00:46:34,490 --> 00:46:36,040
Kenapa hantar surat pun?

648
00:46:36,670 --> 00:46:39,910
- Jujur, tambah dia di LINE lagi senang, kan?
- Alah.

649
00:46:40,060 --> 00:46:42,750
Mungkin terus kena block.

650
00:46:43,360 --> 00:46:47,350
Maew suka tulis surat, jadi dia guna cara dia suka.

651
00:46:47,610 --> 00:46:49,870
Untuk luahkan perasaan pada orang dia suka.

652
00:46:50,130 --> 00:46:51,300
Itu yang paling kena.

653
00:46:51,980 --> 00:46:53,820
Ya, maksud aku—

654
00:46:54,170 --> 00:46:55,470
Menulis surat…

655
00:46:56,070 --> 00:46:58,840
Macam kita renung perasaan sendiri.

656
00:46:59,530 --> 00:47:00,980
Selain dapat—

657
00:47:01,250 --> 00:47:02,970
Tulis pada orang yang kau sayang,

658
00:47:03,290 --> 00:47:04,550
Kau pun jadi lebih faham diri sendiri.

659
00:47:04,830 --> 00:47:07,610
Walaupun dia tak balas surat kau.

660
00:47:07,860 --> 00:47:10,230
Walaupun P’Tonfah tak balas,

661
00:47:10,500 --> 00:47:12,580
Sekurang-kurangnya dia tahu

662
00:47:12,750 --> 00:47:14,160
Ada orang di luar sana suka dia.

663
00:47:14,490 --> 00:47:15,270
Ya.

664
00:47:15,960 --> 00:47:16,750
Betul.

665
00:47:17,100 --> 00:47:19,010
Itu lebih baik daripada suka diam-diam.

666
00:47:19,630 --> 00:47:21,360
Apa maksud kau, suka diam-diam?

667
00:47:21,480 --> 00:47:23,190
Suka dia tapi simpan sorang-sorang.

668
00:47:24,450 --> 00:47:29,520
Kalau kau sayang orang tapi dia tak tahu,
akhirnya untuk apa?

669
00:47:29,800 --> 00:47:35,360
Bagi aku, niat baik ada makna
bila ia sampai pada orang tu.

670
00:47:35,780 --> 00:47:38,010
Hei, hei. Aduh.

671
00:47:42,300 --> 00:47:45,180
Jadi bila kau sedar kau suka P’Jo,

672
00:47:45,360 --> 00:47:46,470
Kau buat apa?

673
00:47:46,960 --> 00:47:48,650
Aku cakap terus terang.

674
00:47:49,400 --> 00:47:50,720
Malah aku bagi gear aku pada dia.

675
00:47:52,140 --> 00:47:54,930
- Dia bagi gear sebelum bercinta lagi.
- Mestilah.

676
00:47:55,020 --> 00:47:56,880
Kalau aku suka dia, kenapa nak tahan?

677
00:47:57,720 --> 00:47:59,150
Aku rasa aku tak mampu buat macam tu.

678
00:47:59,690 --> 00:48:03,180
Kau tak perlu jadi macam aku. Cara kau pun okey.

679
00:48:04,030 --> 00:48:05,550
Jangan fikir banyak dulu.

680
00:48:05,750 --> 00:48:07,850
Tunggu dulu reaksi P’Tonfah.

681
00:48:08,170 --> 00:48:12,630
Kalau dia memang tak selesa, kau boleh undur.

682
00:48:12,980 --> 00:48:14,510
Hah? Undur?

683
00:48:14,650 --> 00:48:16,840
Eh, undur macam tu je?

684
00:48:17,580 --> 00:48:19,290
- Kau baru mula.
- Betul.

685
00:48:20,030 --> 00:48:24,170
Aku rasa kau terus hantar surat macam ni
dan tengok dulu reaksi dia.

686
00:48:24,840 --> 00:48:28,520
Tapi akhirnya, kau kena bagi dia tahu
kau Typhoon yang suka dia.

687
00:48:28,730 --> 00:48:30,170
Bukan sekadar budak sebelah rumah.

688
00:48:31,120 --> 00:48:32,600
Ayuh. Kau boleh.

689
00:48:35,360 --> 00:48:37,850
Jangan fikir banyak, Maew.

690
00:48:38,860 --> 00:48:39,450
Okey tak?

691
00:48:40,170 --> 00:48:44,350
Bila ada mereka, benda berat pun rasa ringan.

692
00:48:45,580 --> 00:48:47,770
Aku rasa macam kau beri aku berkat istimewa, Fun.

693
00:48:48,430 --> 00:48:49,680
Sejak ada kawan,

694
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:52,620
Aku tak rasa ditinggalkan lagi.

695
00:48:53,350 --> 00:48:54,910
Jangan risau, Fun.

696
00:48:55,370 --> 00:48:57,050
Aku lebih kuat sekarang.

697
00:48:57,380 --> 00:49:00,360
Aku makan lebih, tidur lebih,

698
00:49:00,580 --> 00:49:02,360
Senyum dan ketawa,

699
00:49:02,680 --> 00:49:04,200
Dan jauh lebih bahagia.

700
00:49:04,890 --> 00:49:09,270
Dan paling penting, akhirnya aku berani ikut perasaan sendiri.

701
00:49:09,630 --> 00:49:12,730
Lepas ni, terpulang pada P’Fah.

702
00:49:52,160 --> 00:49:54,120
Pagi ni cuaca elok.

703
00:49:54,500 --> 00:49:58,000
Langit cerah, matahari pun tak terik.

704
00:49:58,660 --> 00:50:00,690
Cara yang baik untuk mulakan hari.

705
00:50:00,870 --> 00:50:03,590
Harap awak gembira sepanjang hari.

706
00:50:12,400 --> 00:50:13,060
Mm.

707
00:50:17,610 --> 00:50:19,760
Aku rasa P’Fah tak suka.

708
00:50:22,820 --> 00:50:23,930
Kalau macam tu, aku tak usik kau.

709
00:50:24,690 --> 00:50:26,670
Aku pergi dulu.

710
00:50:35,100 --> 00:50:37,190
Helo? Ya, ya.

711
00:50:38,080 --> 00:50:38,980
Cepatlah, cepat.

712
00:50:42,010 --> 00:50:43,780
Jom, jom.

713
00:51:11,040 --> 00:51:13,560
P’Fah, selamat menjamu selera.

714
00:51:14,200 --> 00:51:15,230
Terima kasih.

715
00:51:21,420 --> 00:51:23,050
Nampak kau lebih okey dari yang aku sangka.

716
00:51:23,600 --> 00:51:24,500
Macam mana tu?

717
00:51:27,770 --> 00:51:29,890
Aku ingat kau dah nak undur diri.

718
00:51:30,270 --> 00:51:31,440
P'Fah tak balas.

719
00:51:31,820 --> 00:51:33,340
Dan ada pesaing lain juga.

720
00:51:35,200 --> 00:51:38,310
Tak seteruk tu, walau aku nak cakap dengan dia.

721
00:51:39,120 --> 00:51:42,140
Kalau setakat ini saja, maka inilah saja.

722
00:51:45,710 --> 00:51:48,140
Kau ingat tak apa kau cakap pada aku, North?

723
00:51:48,750 --> 00:51:51,040
Sekurang-kurangnya sampai pada dia.

724
00:51:52,170 --> 00:51:53,190
Perasaan aku.

725
00:51:56,880 --> 00:51:58,260
Aku lega kau okey.

726
00:52:00,290 --> 00:52:01,900
Kau betul-betul dah matang, Maew.

727
00:52:46,780 --> 00:52:50,340
Jo, tengok Fah. Dia cemburu mengongkong.

728
00:53:02,590 --> 00:53:05,150
Aku rasa kau belum sarapan lagi.

729
00:53:05,520 --> 00:53:09,130
Mungkin kau tertanya kenapa aku selalu bagi sandwic tuna dan susu coklat.

730
00:53:09,530 --> 00:53:11,690
Bukan sebab aku tak tahu nak bagi apa.

731
00:53:12,270 --> 00:53:14,090
Aku cuma rasa benda tu sedap.

732
00:53:51,700 --> 00:53:52,380
Hei.

733
00:53:53,190 --> 00:53:54,260
Kenapa?

734
00:53:55,650 --> 00:53:56,560
Apa ni?

735
00:53:56,970 --> 00:53:58,120
Buka saja.

736
00:54:06,020 --> 00:54:08,500
Susu coklat dan sandwic memang sedap.

737
00:54:08,870 --> 00:54:10,420
Pastikan habiskan.

738
00:54:14,950 --> 00:54:17,470
Dah kantoi.

739
00:54:18,840 --> 00:54:20,200
Jadi, kau suka dia?

740
00:54:20,640 --> 00:54:21,890
Belum sampai tahap suka lagi.

741
00:54:21,970 --> 00:54:23,330
Aku cuma nak kenal dia lebih lagi.

742
00:54:23,720 --> 00:54:25,610
Rasa macam boleh terapung sekarang.

743
00:54:25,700 --> 00:54:28,940
Dia suka kau, atau orang dalam surat tu?

744
00:54:29,530 --> 00:54:32,400
Dia asyik cuba letak batas antara kami.

745
00:54:32,820 --> 00:54:34,760
Tapi aku tak pernah langgar batas tu.

746
00:54:34,990 --> 00:54:37,210
Tengok ni. P'Fah memang tengah mengurat kau.

747
00:54:37,370 --> 00:54:39,460
Jadi macam mana dengan orang yang hantar surat tu?

748
00:54:39,610 --> 00:54:42,060
Aku rasa dia comel juga.

749
00:54:42,340 --> 00:54:43,980
Selamat hari jadi.

750
00:54:44,180 --> 00:54:45,290
Terima kasih.

751
00:54:45,690 --> 00:54:47,510
Kau tak nak tahu siapa dia?

